title: Bear Den [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
You rested in the woods, and couldn't have predicted it would have turned to pure hell. When you went for firewood again, you fell into a hole. Then when you looked around, things started looking creepy. Around lay the gnawed bones and skulls of people, and next to you on the ground lay a machete, a sword with a shield and an onion. You quickly grabbed everything, realizing that you will not have time to think about it. At the same instant, crowds of bears fell from the darkness. Do not let yourself be devoured by the beasts, it's kill or be killed.
